 New York find A Pet with Paws to be a solid choice. This facility features heated spaces for cold New York winters, caring and attentive team members, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. conveniently located in the heart of New York. Visit A Pet with Paws to see their facilities firsthand\",\"slug\":\"a-pet-with-paws\",\"address\":\"30 E 65th St Suite 9D\",\"street\":\"30 E 65th St Suite 9D\",\"city\":\"New York\",\"state\":\"NY\",\"zipCode\":\"10065\",\"full_address\":\"30 E 65th St Suite 9D, New York, NY 10065, USA\",\"latitude\":40.7669885,\"longitude\":-73.96844089999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ77kqI-pZwokRXvR9IUY-_Wo\",\"phone\":\"(917) 664-6079\",\"website\":\"https://www.apetwithpaws.com/\",\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":2,\"userRatingsTotal\":2,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"12:00 – 4:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/a-pet-with-paws/a-pet-with-paws-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/a-pet-with-paws/a-pet-with-paws-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/a-pet-with-paws/a-pet-with-paws-3.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/newyork/a-pet-with-paws/a-pet-with-paws-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}}]\n44:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8 text-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors font-medium\",\"children\":\"Browse All Parks →\"}]